843
01:06:01,000 --> 01:06:02,791
We need to move fast.

844
01:06:02,916 --> 01:06:04,291
Guys, get the Glia.

845
01:06:04,416 --> 01:06:08,083
Once we get it we'll need water
and carbon to complete it, and

846
01:06:08,208 --> 01:06:09,916
