940
01:12:00,416 --> 01:12:02,916
I think
you should really be reasonable.

941
01:12:03,041 --> 01:12:04,500
Your machines may be capable,

942
01:12:04,625 --> 01:12:05,666
but they're no match

943
01:12:05,791 --> 01:12:07,250
